Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.07,0:01:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}奈尔法国境附近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 这是什么玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是团子了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么买这么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 是你买
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.05,0:01:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？关我什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是前几天那失败的赔礼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我毫无意义地潜入堡垒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易找到的勇者遗物不会用还丢下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后你得天天给我买团子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢下不管你不也有份吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.40,0:02:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡几百年的勇者遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.13,0:02:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有那么容易用得来的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且凭啥我就得为此买团子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我买 请让我买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我这么悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 这都是席恩的错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪那小子什么麻烦事都推给我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 现在他一定吃着大餐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠闲地睡午觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}罗兰德城 会议室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次事件 您打算怎么负责
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种说法 对陛下太无礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.38,0:02:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}绝不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 恕臣直言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下太乐观了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐予属国艾斯塔布尔的国王和贵族我国的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至为领民生活提供保障
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是这种态度才会引起叛乱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算boss登场了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他也是为国着想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 您打算如何处理此次叛乱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您能尽快应对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么尽快应对…消息传来才第二天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛军的根据地和主谋都不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对策已经备妥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛乱的主谋也已查明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艾斯塔布尔前国王的独生女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺娅·艾恩公主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详情请收集情报的米兰·弗洛瓦德上校汇报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据情报艾斯塔布尔方的兵力约五万
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五万？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已经不是叛乱了 是战争啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:04:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领地与艾斯塔布尔邻接的大人们有可能被战斗波及
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望诸位暂时在本城内避难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们势必死守诸位的领地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我们离开领地？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任由你这种人践踏我们的领地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事决无可恕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非领地里有什么见不得人的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那倒没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 各位也可以留在领地里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔布尔的势力不过五万而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不足为惧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 之后我将率军一支
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往保卫各领地及镇压叛乱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这次事件交由克拉乌·柯洛姆少将负责
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛瓦德负责情报收集和传达
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辅佐克拉乌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要这种人的支援…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令 克拉乌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛瓦德也听明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场叛乱 是你策划的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让串通者发动叛乱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将艾斯塔布尔的反罗兰德势力一网打尽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便以战争为口实派兵前往各领地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查反国王派贵族们的不正行径吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是如此 您作何打算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你尽自己的本职就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}艾斯塔布尔军 最前线要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王此时还身在罗兰德吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您还在意令尊的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令尊身为我们的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了换取罗兰德提出的地位和安全
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻易便出卖了国家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是觉得 让父王来当叛乱的盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民众会更高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们贵族以及国民 都很仰慕您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是我们新的王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺娅·艾恩殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争 若是败了将会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且罗兰德对艾斯塔布尔人民也施以良政
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有必要战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要将历史悠久的艾斯塔布尔从罗兰德手中…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家什么的并不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是人民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样人民真的能过上幸福日子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不只是白白流血而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要民众能过得幸福就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你教给我的吗 萨拉威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们的势力还很强大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以罗兰德也不敢轻举妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而没有保证今后能维持多久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于罗兰德贵族的恶劣传闻也不绝于耳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若您真心为民着想就要把握时机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你这样说 那就必然没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:06:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是为了您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们情愿付出生命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都过得快乐 所有人都过得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想创造一个这样的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吗 萨拉威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始 我们将和罗兰德开战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了夺回我艾斯塔布尔的独立权
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯洛姆少将传令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs40}克里亚德伯爵领 城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修斯 敌方兵力是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约八、九千吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如弗洛瓦德情报所示
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就以最小限度的牺牲拿下这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军前进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗兰德的走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪儿冒出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种混战没法放大魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪 指挥官在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是这支军队的指挥官吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们艾斯塔布尔的指挥官已经被我杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再行抵抗就杀无赦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血染的红色手指
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“红指克拉乌”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙就是罗兰德的红指克拉乌？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无聊的红指
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说又战败了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直像是我军的动向完全被人看穿了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早说了 这是鲁莽之行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今还说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红指克拉乌…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说罗兰德的指挥官叫克拉乌·柯洛姆对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听闻他尽量不杀我方士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令其不战而降是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.81,0:09:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若那就是罗兰德的战斗方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是英雄王席恩·阿斯塔尔的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这场战争果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定也是敌方的企图
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是为了吞并艾斯塔布尔之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不引起愤怒和怨恨才这样战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有对策
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可示弱 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯洛姆少将的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已包围了叛军根据地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}艾斯塔布尔军 最前线要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗兰德必须退兵 并释放俘虏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不同意以上条件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就每时辰杀一个艾斯塔布尔人民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的信已经送给罗兰德军了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗兰德的英雄王不会对人民见死不救的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了 你竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而事出无奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保护您 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我而将人民当做人质吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为民着想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们若战败后果不堪设想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战败国的人民将会遭到何等的欺凌羞辱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以人民为人质 难道就不算欺凌人民吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能阻止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是被推上台的傀儡王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来救不了任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗兰德的军队…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我军的士兵正在进攻艾斯塔布尔的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我军的士兵全都在此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？那是哪里的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陛下送来的援军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩说全权交由我负责的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:11:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能会这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成 是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红指克拉乌竟然会无视人质进行攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以人民为人质还被打败的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是死刑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不一定战败
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害人质吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗兰德以为我们不是说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要杀了人质…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家已经很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,释放人质吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我一人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万万不可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能让公主殿下独自去送死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,属下…也与公主殿下共生死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,属下也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你们这句话就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位请活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:13:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着 努力让艾斯塔布尔人民过的幸福一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位忧国忧民的心意感人肺腑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 依鄙人之见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺娅·艾恩公主殿下一人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要补偿这次的罪孽似乎略显不足
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要装点艾斯塔布尔一国灭亡悲剧的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然还是悲剧最合适 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是罗兰德帝国军上校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米兰·弗洛瓦德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的士兵全灭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座城堡到底没那么容易攻陷的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说就算攻陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会让罗兰德士兵进城的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里即将上演悲剧的最后一幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗影现形
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 不能丢下大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去里面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家 人民
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说还有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被逼上绝路的艾斯塔布尔失去理智
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至开始杀害人质
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉威尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了理智的就是您 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而手刃疯狂的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束这场战争的艾斯塔布尔贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉威尔·塞伊尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会成为救国英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为罗兰德所接受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我军的动向泄露出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要挟持人质的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是你干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那么相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本的计划是娶您为妻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篡夺这个国家的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…想创造一个所有人都能过得开心的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜言蜜语是无法操纵世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此…即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 您真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您放心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:16:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗兰德还不至于缺英雄缺到让这种人当英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是罗兰德的英雄王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩·阿斯塔尔的所作所为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾王自然不齿这种行径
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的事完全是我独断专行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 和萨拉威尔相勾结
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煽动我们发动叛乱的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而王却看破一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任命柯洛姆少将而非我镇压叛乱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾王就是这样的伟人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 正如萨拉威尔先生所言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜言蜜语无法操纵世界也是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺娅·艾恩公主杀害人质之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自行了断
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是我的剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯塔尔王会原谅你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好是能瞒天过海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过应该会原谅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是身为王的器量…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你竟是叛乱的主谋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真服了您 柯洛姆少将
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到您来得这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯洛姆少将？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说他就是红指克拉乌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据回答…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定是否杀了我 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩果然不需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看不到那位大人所背负的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒是你没资格侍奉陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要待在席恩身边根本不需要什么资格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了那位大人即将走上的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要杀掉诺娅·艾恩殿下和人质
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你要阻挠…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你能拿我怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小事一桩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:17:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了艾斯塔布尔人民
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不能失去这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗影…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛瓦德！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛瓦德上校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若为了完全支配艾斯塔布尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须杀害人质
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我来说服他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去说服人民和士兵都服从罗兰德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起杀害人质降低艾斯塔布尔的评价
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这样做更为有效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你在艾斯塔布尔人民之中很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 或许也会有人叱责你是卖国贼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后杀了我也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请不要杀害大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争已经结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请撤兵吧 柯洛姆少将
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:18:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信…你和你的王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯洛姆少将
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎没力气了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能麻烦您拉我站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是您
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔布尔人民一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又让克拉乌杀了人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 这场战争是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没有追究弗洛瓦德的罪责
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让克拉乌率军
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了尽可能增加获救的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不过是给自己找的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩哥哥你在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在图书上看过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是快要哭的表情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉丝还是第一次看见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝姐姐从来不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西尔哥哥别说哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是一脸阴笑的吓死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西尔的确很可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐你要哭吗 哭吗哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫不是伊莉丝碍着你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下次 下次要哭的时候一定要给我看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 你不是来报告莱纳和菲莉丝的事的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…狗是莱纳 天使是菲莉丝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 禽兽君和完全和谐美少女天使菲莉丝姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.30,0:20:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖洞的时候挖出个短剑样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道怎么回事扔了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:20:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就长出龙来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是勇者遗物？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 米拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可属实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供情报的是他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于他您很了解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.60,0:21:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉丝 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能麻烦你立即回莱纳他们身边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那莱纳 今天的份靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团子团子团子团子团子！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩这…席恩这…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止说这么低级的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:23.51,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}制作：akira 安静の云
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.71,0:23:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？重新调查之前那勇者遗物？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.52,0:23:26.85,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}漫游字幕组\Nhttp://popgo.net/bbs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.70,0:23:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干 麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正去了也是一堆麻烦事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}忘却碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.53,0:23:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真是麻烦
